<p>
<note n="0116001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116001">唯＝惟【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0116002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116002">緣＝斷【三】</note>
<note n="0116003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116003">〔大毘婆沙論〕－【明】</note>
<note n="0116004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116004">為＝謂【明】</note>
<note n="0117001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117001">蹬＝隥【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0117002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117002">〔後〕－【三】【宮】</note>
